# For her daughter's birthday Ludmila has decided to organize a party to which she invites all her
# classmates. For this purpose, she has decided to rent an entertainment hall for children, whose rent you will receive as an entrance from
# the console.
# Write a program to help Ludmila calculate what budget she will need.

venue_price = float(input())
cake_price = float(venue_price * 0.20)
drink_price = float(cake_price * 0.55)
funTime_price = float(venue_price / 1/3)
buget_value = float(venue_price + cake_price + drink_price + funTime_price)
print(buget_value)
